cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV. 

The paper deals with the navigation problem for a robot amidst static and dynamic obstacles, which is a typical problem in robotics. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics). The paper also proposes a hierarchical approach to solve the problem, which involves both path planning and path following control. This suggests that the paper may also belong to cs.SY (Systems and Control) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also proposes enhancements to the path planning algorithm, which may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.CV (Computer Vision) depending on the nature of the enhancements.
